entry.string: SELECT USD.Username, USD.FullName, FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE, USD.Birthday)/365) AS Age, USD.Gender, DATE_FORMAT(USD.dateRegistered, '%Y-%m-%d') AS dateRegistered FROM Account AS ACT, UserDetails AS USD WHERE ACT.userId = USD.userId AND ACT.active = true AND #[flowVars.userId] = USD.userId

SELECT USD.Username, USD.FullName, FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE, USD.Birthday)/365) AS Age, USD.Gender, DATE_FORMAT(USD.dateRegistered, '%Y-%m-%d') AS dateRegistered FROM Account AS ACT, UserDetails AS USD WHERE ACT.userId = USD.userId AND ACT.active = true

SELECT USD.Username, USD.FullName, USD.Birthday, USD.Gender, DATE_FORMAT(USD.dateRegistered, '%Y-%m-%d') AS dateRegistered FROM Account AS ACT, UserDetails AS USD WHERE ACT.userId = USD.userId AND ACT.active = true AND #[message.inboundProperties.] = USD.userId

SELECT USD.Username, USD.FullName, USD.Birthday, USD.Gender, DATE_FORMAT(USD.dateRegistered, '%Y-%m-%d') AS dateRegistered FROM Account AS ACT, UserDetails AS USD WHERE ACT.userId = USD.userId AND ACT.active = true

SELECT USD.Username, USD.FullName, USD.Birthday, USD.Gender, DATE_FORMAT(USD.dateRegistered, '%Y-%m-%d') AS dateRegistered FROM Account AS ACT, UserDetails AS USD WHERE ACT.userId = USD.userId AND ACT.active = true AND #[flowVars.userId] = USD.userId

SELECT USD.Username, USD.FullName, USD.Birthday, USD.Gender, DATE_FORMAT(USD.dateRegistered, '%Y-%m-%d') AS dateRegistered FROM Account AS ACT, UserDetails AS USD WHERE ACT.userId = USD.userId AND ACT.active = true AND #[message.inboundProperties.'http.request.uri'.userId] = USD.userId
SELECT USD.Username, USD.FullName, USD.Birthday, USD.Gender, USD.dateRegistered FROM Account AS ACT, UserDetails AS USD WHERE ACT.userId = USD.userId AND ACT.active = true
